<view>
    <view class="header">
        <image src="../../../assets/images/lylj-ing-icon.jpg"></image>
        <text>寻找设备中，请耐心等待...</text>
    </view>
    <view class="inner"  hidden="{{true}}">
        <view class="before" hidden="{{true}}">
            <image src="../../../assets/images/lylj-null-icon.jpg"></image>
            <text>请确保待绑定设备在手机旁边</text>
            <text>并且已经开机</text>
        </view>
        <view class="after">
            <image src="../../../assets/images/lylj-result-icon.jpg"></image>
            <text>罗氏Connect血糖仪</text>
            <text class="no-text">00:60:19:40:3D:60</text>
        </view>
        <view class="form-button"
              data-url="bluetooth_add_index"
              bindtap="handleJump">
            <text class="form-button-text">绑定</text>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view hidden="{{true}}">
        <view class="tel">
            <text>如有问题，您可以拨打罗氏客户关爱热线</text>
            <text class="tel-text">800 820 2777（固话）</text>
            <text class="tel-text">400 820 2777（手机）</text>
            <text>工作时间每天8：00-20：00（法定节假日除外）</text>
        </view>
        <view class="prompt">
            <text>部分安卓机型，无法正常使用蓝牙连接</text>
            <view class="link"
                  data-url="record_index"
                  bindtap="handleJump">
                <text>点击前往手动记录</text>
            </view>
        </view>
    </view>

    <view class="pop-wrap" hidden="{{true}}">
        <view class="pop-inner">
            <text class="pop-title">蓝牙配对请求</text>
            <view class="pop-prompt">
                <text class="color">“Performa Connect血糖仪”</text><text>想与您的手机配对，请输入血糖仪上显示的代码</text>
            </view>
            <input class="pop-input" type="number"/>
            <view class="pop-btn">
                <view class="pop-btn-item">
                    <text>取消</text>
                </view>
                <view class="pop-btn-item">
                    <text>配对</text>
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>
    </view>
</view>
